<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>圆觉经 - 标签 - 无名老人</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E5%9C%86%E8%A7%89%E7%BB%8F/</link><description>无名老人的文章</description><generator>Hugo 0.160.1 &amp; FixIt v0.4.5</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/tags/%E5%9C%86%E8%A7%89%E7%BB%8F/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>昧佛义者</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%98%A7%E4%BD%9B%E4%B9%89%E8%80%85-%E9%99%A4%E8%8B%A6%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%98%A7%E4%BD%9B%E4%B9%89%E8%80%85-%E9%99%A4%E8%8B%A6%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="昧佛义者除苦何在"&gt;&lt;span&gt;昧佛义者，除苦何在&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%98%a7%e4%bd%9b%e4%b9%89%e8%80%85%e9%99%a4%e8%8b%a6%e4%bd%95%e5%9c%a8" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：世间皆苦、四相、依法不依人、无所得、佛知见、大般涅槃经、圆觉经、四依、惭愧、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　邪法增炽的末世群盲，要想修学佛之正法，就应知“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;世间皆苦&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”是佛初始所讲的法语，是告诉我们，认家为己，认假为真的众生，为了护执这个不是我的我的形象，是离不开口善心恶，言正心邪所自造自受的集累业力的苦果，如此也就不知因果不爽之“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;报&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”，所以身不由己的迷执“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;四相&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”，于是各顾各的心态是不会相信“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;世间皆苦&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”的。不相信者又怎知其真实义呢？我执当先必迷恋小乘有为之法。正因如此才会总以自卑的苦水或自傲的乐水浇灭心智之火。心中的觉智无从开启，那就只有与蠢相伴，与邪念暗恶相处。苦者，自造嫉妒、嗔恨苦水自伤，以累业增苦为行；乐者，自受邪慢骄慢远离自性之真。苦者无惭，乐者无愧，常因嗔恨而指责他人，造业增苦而不能自知，虚生浪死岂能自出。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>能观心者</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%83%E8%80%85-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 15:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%83%BD%E8%A7%82%E5%BF%83%E8%80%85-%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%A7%A3%E8%84%B1/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="能观心者究竟解脱"&gt;&lt;span&gt;能观心者，究竟解脱&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%83%bd%e8%a7%82%e5%bf%83%e8%80%85%e7%a9%b6%e7%ab%9f%e8%a7%a3%e8%84%b1" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：观心、解脱、本心、佛性、大乘、法华经、大般涅槃经、圆觉经、于相离相、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　能观心者，究竟解脱，不能观者，究竟沉沦。何以故？经曰“&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;不识本心，学法无益&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;”故。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>离四病者</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E7%A6%BB%E5%9B%9B%E7%97%85%E8%80%85-%E6%8A%A4%E4%BC%A0%E6%AD%A3%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 13:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E7%A6%BB%E5%9B%9B%E7%97%85%E8%80%85-%E6%8A%A4%E4%BC%A0%E6%AD%A3%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="离四病者方可称为护传正法的善师"&gt;&lt;span&gt;离四病者，方可称为护传正法的善师&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e7%a6%bb%e5%9b%9b%e7%97%85%e8%80%85%e6%96%b9%e5%8f%af%e7%a7%b0%e4%b8%ba%e6%8a%a4%e4%bc%a0%e6%ad%a3%e6%b3%95%e7%9a%84%e5%96%84%e5%b8%88" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：圆觉经、普觉菩萨、四病、作病、任病、止病、灭病、善知识、佛知见、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　《圆觉经》中，普觉菩萨代末世众生请问世尊：求何等人？依何等法？行何等行？除去何病？云何发心？佛告以当求一切正知见人，心不住相，不著声闻缘觉境界，虽现尘劳，心恒清净，示有诸过，赞叹梵行。并指出彼善智师所证妙法，应离作、任、止、灭四病。今依经义，详述四病之相及离病之要，愿诸佛子择善师、离四病，成就无上菩提。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>苦口良药，逆耳忠言</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%8B%A6%E5%8F%A3%E8%89%AF%E8%8D%AF%E9%80%86%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%A0%E8%A8%80/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Apr 2026 11:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E8%8B%A6%E5%8F%A3%E8%89%AF%E8%8D%AF%E9%80%86%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%A0%E8%A8%80/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="苦口良药逆耳忠言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;苦口良药，逆耳忠言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e8%8b%a6%e5%8f%a3%e8%89%af%e8%8d%af%e9%80%86%e8%80%b3%e5%bf%a0%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：大般涅槃经、法华经、圆觉经、放逸、涅槃、佛知见、四依法、修行、觉悟、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;　　苦口才是良药，逆耳方是忠言。改过必生智慧，护短心内非贤。此理虽浅，行之实难。末世学佛众，若真欲出离生死，当依佛之知见，莫被文字所缚，莫被情见所迷。今依经义，略述如下。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>正观经文</title><link>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%96%87-%E5%8F%91%E6%95%91%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E4%BC%97%E7%94%9F%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2014 01:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://vanvj00002.github.io/monkvan/posts/%E6%AD%A3%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F%E6%96%87-%E5%8F%91%E6%95%91%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E4%BC%97%E7%94%9F%E5%BF%83/</guid><description>&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h1 class="heading-element" id="正观经文方能正受经文佛义谈发救一切众生心"&gt;&lt;span&gt;正观经文，方能正受经文佛义——谈“发救一切众生心”&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e6%ad%a3%e8%a7%82%e7%bb%8f%e6%96%87%e6%96%b9%e8%83%bd%e6%ad%a3%e5%8f%97%e7%bb%8f%e6%96%87%e4%bd%9b%e4%b9%89%e8%b0%88%e5%8f%91%e6%95%91%e4%b8%80%e5%88%87%e4%bc%97%e7%94%9f%e5%bf%83" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;关键词&lt;/strong&gt;：发救一切众生心、佛知见、自性佛、般若波罗蜜、不二心、同体大悲、六祖、法华经、圆觉经、无取无舍&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="前言"&gt;&lt;span&gt;前言&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#%e5%89%8d%e8%a8%80" class="heading-mark"&gt;
